Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there books on shelves?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there books on shelves?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the floor made of wood?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the floor made of wood?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
